FBIS4-14617 "drsov063_u_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-063 Daily Report 31 Mar 1994 Latvia Foreign Debt for First Quarter Reported Foreign Debt for First Quarter Reported LD3103165894 Riga Radio Riga Network in Latvian 1500 GMT 31 Mar 94 LD3103165894 Riga Radio Riga Network Latvian BFN [Text] According to approximate calculations by the foreign economic relations department of the Ministry of Finance, the Latvian foreign debt up to 31 March of this year has reached more than $200 million and not $320 million U.S. dollars, as was envisaged. The reduction in the foreign debt is connected to the envisaged foreign country credits not being received during the first quarter of this year.
